SELECT nt.symbol, nt.trade_date, nt.neural_network_output, nt.trade_decision, ht.trade_price FROM neural_network_trading nt JOIN historical_trades ht ON nt.symbol = ht.symbol WHERE nt.trade_decision = 'Buy' AND ht.trade_price BETWEEN 50 AND 200 ORDER BY nt.trade_date DESC;

SELECT * FROM backtest_results WHERE return_rate > 0.05 ORDER BY return_rate DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM trade_data WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY volume DESC;

SELECT trading_strategy.strategy_name, backtest_results.win_rate FROM trading_strategy INNER JOIN backtest_results ON trading_strategy.id = backtest_results.strategy_id WHERE backtest_results.win_rate > 0.8;
SELECT neural_network.model_name, trade_data.date, trade_data.close_price FROM neural_network LEFT JOIN trade_data ON neural_network.id = trade_data.neural_network_id WHERE trade_data.volume > 10000;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_trades, SUM(backtest_results.profit) AS total_profit FROM backtest_results WHERE backtest_results.profit > 0;

SELECT trading_strategy.strategy_name, AVG(neural_network.accuracy) AS avg_accuracy FROM trading_strategy INNER JOIN neural_network ON trading_strategy.id = neural_network.strategy_id GROUP BY trading_strategy.strategy_name ORDER BY avg_accuracy DESC;
